Durban - Scores of people have been treated for injuries sustained in a number of road crashes across Durban on Monday. 
 

 
  Emergency crews had their hands full, attending to various crashes. 
 
 
  
 
 
  The M4 near Sibaya has been partially closed as part of the roadway has collapsed. 
  Motorists are urged to drive carefully. 
 
 
  
 
 
  
   







